responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "A9D79D744D459B4F2ABFBD86E06C0AF4", "Ah, you must reach the Ancestral Hollow, but the road is not so easily found. To the north, where the earth and sky meet, the road waits for those not seeking it. To the east, the earth holds what was, silent and unmoving, beyond both space and time. The path lies where few tread, hidden from those who seek too eagerly. It waits for the worthy, those who are called, and there the way will reveal itself when the time is right.")
